282
00:26:56,790 --> 00:26:58,160
Sme hotoví.

283
00:26:58,160 --> 00:26:59,960
Tak sa vráťme späť do OZ.

284
00:27:00,990 --> 00:27:02,900
Tao Le Si.

285
00:27:04,300 --> 00:27:06,500
