318
00:29:51,250 --> 00:29:53,690
Nepôjdeš za šéfkou?

319
00:29:55,240 --> 00:29:57,080
Nevidíš?

320
00:29:57,080 --> 00:29:59,750
Nateraz to zvládne sama.

321
00:30:10,350 --> 00:30:12,060
Som doma.

322
00:30:12,060 --> 00:30:13,870
Práve včas.

323
00:30:13,870 --> 00:30:16,790
